value.0: You've made short work of my creatures. It would not be wise to let you do the same to me.

As for my partners, I barely spoke to most of them. However, I do know that Zor is an idiot and has likely drowned himself in an ale barrel at the Green Griffon Inn. It was to be his first stop. It's on the road North of Port Llast, you can't miss it.
